<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10547" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="NEW">Change Data Binding</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1054B" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW"><ahelp hid=".">Edit the data binding in the XForms <link href="text/shared/01/xformsdata.xhp">Data Navigator</link>.</ahelp><comment>UFI: called from the control's context menu</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN1056E" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Model</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN10572" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW"><ahelp hid=".">Select the name of the XForms model.</ahelp><comment>UFI: ?? not in spec</comment></paragraph>
<paragraph role="heading" id="par_idN10587" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="NEW">Item list</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_idN1058B" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="NEW"><ahelp hid=".">Displays the data binding for the selected form control. To change the data binding, select another item in the list click <emph>OK</emph>. To access the <emph>Add</emph> and <emph>Properties</emph> commands for an item, right-click the item.</ahelp></paragraph>
